content: The wrestler who has cashed in the most Money in the Bank contracts so far is Carmella. She has cashed in her contract twice, once in 2018 to win the SmackDown Women's Championship and once in 2020 to win the 24/7 Championship. Other wrestlers who have cashed in their contracts more than once include Edge, CM Punk, and Seth Rollins, who have all had successful cash-ins twice.
